<caaml:SnowProfile xmlns:caaml="http://caaml.org/Schemas/SnowProfileIACS/v6.0.3" xmlns:gml="http://www.opengis.net/gml" xmlns:slf="http://www.slf.ch/snowprofile/1.0" gml:id="87180078-c5d7-49c5-abb6-7d26e3590974"><caaml:metaData><caaml:customData><slf:profiletext-list><slf:profiletext key="TEXT_BLOCK_DEFAULT"><slf:text>UTM coordinates: 462'400 / 7'732'800

PROFILE LOCATION
----------------
Skier's left of the couloir leading from the col between the Trolltinden and the Storejaegervastinden down to the Trollbreen. Extremely steep northern aspect. Location below a rock, sheltered from shoots. Representative for steep northern aspects. Snowdepth at profile location below average (with respect to bowl).
Please find UTM coordinates in header.

PROFILE
-------
The slab sits on older faceted crystals followed by well settled, harder layers below. In general, the layering is favorable. The slab is rather thin and although it supports fracture propagation, no signs of instability were observed in the bowl. The variability of the snow surface is strong due to steep shoots releasing sluffs and falling ice from the rock faces.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
The ECT showed full propagation on the the third tap from the ellbow.

SNOW SURFACE
------------
Smooth, dry and soft at the profile. Soft, dry snow in the steep northern aspects. Rest of the bowl variable with crusts and old accumulations. Southern and western aspects became slushy to about 1200m by 14:00 already.

SNOW DRIFT
----------
No new snow drifts.

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
No signs observed today.

AVALANCHES
----------
No avalanching observed.

AVALANCHE DANGER
----------------
low, increasing to moderate with daytime warming

RUTSCHBLOCK TEST
----------------
Layer@96.0: ECT 13/13 

ECT #1
------
Layer@96.0: full propagation</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2015-04-27T17:20:00+02:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2015-04-27T21:18:11+02:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2015-04-27T21:54:19+02:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Norwegen - Lyngen - Storejaegervastinden</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>1225</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>N</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>49</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.739021 46.128036</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">122.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-6.6</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">122.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">4.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>RG</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>FC</caaml:grainFormSecondary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>0.5</caaml:avg></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F-4F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">4.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm